{"3858480": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "忍法！~色色忍法帖~", "steam_appid": 3858480, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>遊戲概述</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《忍法！~色色忍法帖~》是一款3D動作冒險RPG。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >來自異界的淫魔族大舉入侵...！把整個人界攪得天翻地覆...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家將在和風的地圖裡體驗好色忍者「紗奈」的大冒險♥</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3858480/extras/5ce8458bc3dd2b395e81d390499d3fe9.poster.avif?t=1776415713\" width=1080 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3858480/extras/5ce8458bc3dd2b395e81d390499d3fe9.webm?t=1776415713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3858480/extras/5ce8458bc3dd2b395e81d390499d3fe9.mp4?t=1776415713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>人物介紹</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>紗奈｜忍者</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隸屬退魔公會，專門接手高風險、高報酬的討伐任務。<br>她的目標非常單純，就是賺錢、賺很多錢，然後早早實現財富自由！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >至於守護正義？世界和平？<br>抱歉，那些她一點興趣也沒有。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >比起榮耀與使命，紗奈更喜歡的，是任務結束後獎金入袋時，那清脆又迷人的聲音。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，這樣愜意又現實的忍者人生，卻在某天被打破。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >來自退魔公會的緊急任務！讓紗奈的命運齒輪開始轉動……<br>只是這次的任務，似乎不只需要忍術與武力，還得動用她那「特殊的戰鬥」的技巧？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3858480/extras/c3ea3925e4a432fb062d266ad404b1c0.avif?t=1776415713\" width=600 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>玩法介紹</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>全3D冒險 × 關卡挑戰</strong></p></li></ul><p clas